data.description:
Located on approximately 180 acres of breathtaking land, this steel-framed farmhouse offers a peaceful and serene lifestyle with abundant natural beauty. The 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom, 1580 sq ft home built in 2000 features a spacious open floor plan, perfect for comfortable living and entertaining.

As you enter, you'll appreciate the well-designed layout with all bedrooms thoughtfully placed on the main floor for easy access. At the heart of the home, a loft overlooks the living area, offering a versatile space that could be utilized as a game room/office space. Located on each side of the loft are additional spaces that would be perfect for future bedrooms. 

The exterior of the property is adorned with beautifully crafted stone decorative flower beds. The lush landscape surrounding the house creates a peaceful oasis, perfect for relaxation and enjoyment.

The sprawling land encompasses a perfect blend of wooded areas and pasture land, providing ample opportunities for exploration and outdoor activities. Nature enthusiasts will be delighted by the abundant wildlife, including deer and turkey.

A highlight of this property is a picturesque pond, perfect for fishing, picnicking, or simply enjoying the tranquility of the surroundings. Additionally, you'll find a cozy hunting cabin ideal for retreating from the hectic pace of everyday life.

In terms of additional amenities, this property doesn't disappoint. There is a spacious shop of 1200 sq ft, complete with 220 electric and a storage room. A dog kennel with well water for easy cleanup  Furthermore, a cattle barn with working pens adds convenience for any agricultural pursuits. 

To add to the overall versatility of this property, there is an additional septic tank and electric hookup available, offering possibilities for expansion or other future endeavors.

Don't miss this extraordinary opportunity to own your own slice of paradise. Enchanting and versatile, it is a true gem waiting to be discovered.
